# Getting Started

## Installation

```bash
pip install {{ project_name }}
```

## Basic Usage

```python
import flet as ft
from {{ package_name }} import {{ control_name }}

def main(page: ft.Page):
    page.title = "{{ control_name }} Example"

    page.add(
        {{ control_name }}(
            width=200,
            height=200,
        ),
    )

ft.run(main)
```

